      "writtenOn": "2019-07-31T18:34:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "this seems to imply that all args in all apps we will deploy to GKE going forward will cargo-cult this line. GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS seems standard https://developers.google.com/identity/protocols/application-default-credentials\nVadim, WDYT about standardizing on it in code instead of passing it in args?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 103,
        "startChar": 42,
        "endLine": 103,
        "endChar": 75
      },
      "revId": "9925ebcfe929c0c07d96d9cddcecfd69b1052d66",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
