      "side": 1,
      "message": "clarifying some general principles that should help answering questions like \"Do you prefer for this CL to deal with it in code or to inline the args into the image (or something else)?\" in the future. I definitely prefer this CL not to grow, including adding code here. I\u0027d rather prefer it to shrink, as I\u0027ve suggested earlier today (exclude authentication aspect altogether), if it helps landing things that we\u0027ve agreed on sooner. Another general principle: we don\u0027t have to solve all problems at the same time. It is fine to ignore the auth problem in this CL. The purpose of this CL seems to be initial code and the docker file.\n\npassing command line arg sgtm. Whether to do this in this CL or another - leaving this to you.\n\n---\n\nmy question to Vadim above still stands. Repeating: Vadim, how can we reduce duplication in other GKE apps? It seems that all deployment.yaml files will have to have this line. Are you thinking of solving this with kustomize? I.e. ideally there is only one place where implements passing of the creds.",
